# CHLA Project Workflow

Follow `AGENTS.md` for the shared repo workflow and `CURSOR.md` for the Cursor session flow.

## Always

- Keep changes scoped and avoid broad rewrites.
- Never add secrets, credentials, or production-only values to code or docs.
- Use source-of-truth docs instead of guessing commands or environment details.

## Frontend

- Use Vue Composition API patterns.
- Prefer composables, stores, and focused components over adding more logic to `map-frontend/src/views/MapView.vue`.

## Backend

- Use `python3` for Django commands.
- Keep configuration environment-driven.
- Add explicit migrations for schema changes.

## Verify

- Run the smallest relevant check before handoff.
- Use `./scripts/quick-test.sh` for fast smoke coverage when it fits the change.
